author: Aditya  Mishra

text: Aur Khandu bhai. Apan to 1st year me hi saath me classes krte the. Us samay to har jagah aapke saath hi jaate the, ya hm kahe aapke cycle ke peeche baitha ke :p. Bhai aap jitna hmko cycle pr ghumaye hai naa uska 1/10th bhi koi nhi leke chala hoga. Kaise kr lete the etna bojh uthake abhi bhi nhi samjh aata. Wo MTH ke classes abhi bhi yaad hai hmko, aap ekdum dhyaan se class me padhte the aur questions solve krte the, aur hm whi bagal me baith ke soo jaate the. Abhi bhi yaad hai aapka notes dekh kr usko apne writing me extrapolate krte the, jaise ki kabhi likhenge wapas se. Aur phir kabhi khol ke bhi nhi dekhe xD. Wo aman ka bhi kya mazze lete the hm dono milke, hm to jaante bhi nhi the unko pehle se. Pura 1st year apan saath me hi baithe hai, aur uske baad hm jyada class to gaye hi nhi to, ye atleast hm to bol hi sakte hai ki hm class me sabse jyada baar aapke saath hi baithe hai. Kya time tha bhai wo, aapka pura 1st year ka RR jhele hai apan :p. Uske baad to summers to alag level hi tha, daily jaate the RM aur bakwaas krke aa jate the. Wo to 2nd year me apna room door pad gaya, warna apne bagal wale aadmi ko kitna pareshaan krte hai wo to aap quarantine me dekh hi chuke hoonge. Quarantine me to bina matlab aapke room aa jaate the, mast aapko disturb krna. Waise 4 saal tk aapko bahut maggu maggu bulaye hai, jo ki aap deserve bhi krte the, but mazak nhi jab bhi kisi ko disturb krne ka mann krta tha aapko jarur krte the hm, aur uske baad pata nhi kyu but man pura halka ho jaata tha :p. Wo diwali wala bomb yaad hai naa. Mera waise aapko ek baar bheengana bacha hi reh gaya hai, jo aap 2020 ke ending me kiye the xD, and the rest is history. Jab pata chala tha naa ki aapka placement nhi laga tha 1.1 me, to bura to bahut laga tha kyuki aap bahut jyada deserving the bhai. Lakin uske baad pura time bas aapka kahi se khabar mil jaaye yahi try krte rehte the. Aapko call nhi krte the ki kahi busy naa ho, ya koi kharaab interview ke baare me puch ke aapka mood na kharaab ho jaye, lakin aapka pal pal ka jankaari rakhte the bhai hm. Aur jis din aapka call aaya ki bhai ally me US ka offer aaya bhai, dil se khushi hua tha hmko. Aur es baat ka bhi bahut acha laga ki aap hmko call kiye the, puchne ki kya krna hai aage. Aur hm ussi tone me bole the ki ‚Äògadhe ke bachhe chup chaap offer le lijiye‚Äô :p. Last ka mahina bhi kya mast rha tha bhai. Wo wala accent me aapka bolne pr kitna liye the, aur lete hi rhenge ab to aur bhi. Aur bhai wo ‚Äògreen apple‚Äô wala din ko to kaise hi bhul sakte hai, jitna sunaye hmko sach bole to bura nhi laga, kyuki hm jaante the us samay chahe aap hmko jo bhi bol lijiye, aap dil se to hmko apna bahut acha dost hi mante hai, aur eska validation nhi chahiye hmko bas pata hai. Thanks bhai sab cheez ke liye, aapke bina mera college life pura nhi hota, aapko kabhi nhi bhula payenge bhai hm. Ek khaas sa hi jagah rhega mere dil me aapke liye. Best of Luck bhai for the future, jldi US jaaye aur hmko bhi bulaye xD.  Aur ab to RR kam kijiye bhai :p.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text: Aur kattappa, 1st year me hi aapse dosti ho gya tha, wo bhi acha hua. Warna hm kanpur me hi bahar nhi nikalte. Jitni baar campus se bahar gaye hai aap to constant hi the. Etna plan banate hai mazze krne ka ki mat puchiye. IITk ke sabse bade party planner hai aap to, aapke bina party ka mazza hi nhi aata hai. Hmko bigadne me bahut bada haath aapka hi tha :p. Har baar bahar jaate the to hm kuch na kuch bhul hi jaate the, still har baar bahar jaane se pehle aap mere se jarur puchte the. Apna saath me koi trip nhi ho paaya abhi tk, but hopefully future me bahut hoonge. Wo raat  raat bhar aake aapko aur anany ko room me kitna disturb krte the, us din bahut sunate the. Daily aap dono bolte the ki kal se room band kr denge , phir mast agle din hm wapas aa jate the. Kya din the yaar wo. Diwali ke ek hafte baad kaise aapke room me hm log atom bomb laga ke bhaag gaye the, aap uthe bhi nhi bas karwat badal ke so gaye the xD. Aapke saath to kitna bina matlab ka debate kiye hai apan. Asli bulla session to ye sab tha. Thanks bhai sab cheez ke liye, Bahut mazak udaye mera aap but aapke bina mazza bhi nhi aata college me. Pure covid ke dauran, aap aur ram ka grp me baap bete ka ladai was the most interesting part of those days. Har baar jab bhi grp kholte ek smile ke saath grp band krte the. Thanks Bhai sab cheez ke liye, aur all the best for the future.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text: Gulati Sir Pranaam. Aap jaisa chaapu banda to aaj tk nhi dekhe. Aap jitne jagah involved rehte hai naa, utna mere 4 log milake bhi nhi kr payenge. IDK aap jaisa chaapu aadmi ka mere jaisa dhep se dosti kaise hua, but agar nhi hota to mera college experience adhoora reh jaata. Aaj tk jitne baar aapse mile hai, aap kuch naa kuch naya bata hi dete hai. Ab jab ye sab yaad kr rhe hai, aapka wo ‚ÄòArrey Mishraji‚Äô wala tone ekdum yaad aata rehta hai . Bahut jyada helpful aadmi hai aap, kabhi bhi kisi ka bhi madad krne ke liye tayaar rehte hai aap. Aur aapke bitching partner banne me to alag hi mazza aata hai. Aapke bina to mera degree literally khataam nhi ho pata. Wo Algo 2 ka discussions, ToC me pura endsem chapwa dena, saare eng exams me pass karwana, etc. Bhai humesha miss krenge aapka wo ‚ÄòMishraji aaj free hai kya aap?‚Äô wala calls. Jis din ye call aaya hai us din bahut mazza aaya hai. Although hm kitne baar aapka plan me late aate the, still aap hmko nhi bhul the the <3. Arrey apna to fav TV series bhi same hai. Ab hmko jldi jldi US aana hai aur phir wapas se ye sab masti shuru ho jayega. Abhi bahut TT matches haarna bacha hai, aur bahut vegan chicken treats bhi. Love you bhai ü•∞.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Aur bhai amiiteeshh. Aap dil ke bahut ache aadmi hai bhai. Aaj tk hmko jb bhi kuch jarurat pada hai, bas aapko bol dete hai. Aap ekdum bade bhai jaisa khayaal rakhte the bhai mera. Bahut life lesson bhi diye hai bhai hmko to aap. Wo B-Mid ke raat ke walks yaad hai, bade mazedaar the wo bhi. Jab bhi thoda mood off rehta tha bhai, aapke pass aake random cheez discuss krne lagte the, aur aapke room se jab nikalte the to pata nhi kyu sab sorted lagta tha. Ek apnapan lagta thaa aapke saath to bhai. Kabhi bhi bahar jaana hota tha, bhale hi aur cycle sab rehti thi but aapse maangne ka alag hi mazza hota tha. Aur bhai jo movies dekhi hai hmne randomly uske to kya hi kehne. End me margo ko wo bande ke saath hona chahiye tha xD. Cards khelne me to alag mazza aata tha, kitne baar to hm aapse pura cards cheen lete the, aur aap khushi khushi de dete the. Aur phir hm pura game hagne ke baad aapke pass wapas aate the ki ab bataye kya krna hai, aur aap wapas se hmko batane lagte the. Etna irritate kiye aapko to pata nhi aap kaise mere pr aaj tk gussa nhi hue. Hmko to pura vishwaas hai aap IAS ban ke rahiyega, bas thoda rigorous padhai krte rahiye. Aur aapko to bole hi hai kabhi bhi kuch bhi chahiye hoga to bas ek call milana hai. Aapke liye kuch bhi bhai.
Love You More Dhep <3

PS: Kabhi hm bhi badminton me apko harayenge.

text: Aur bhai anany !!!
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Anany yaar 4 saal me sabse jyada aapke saath hi waqt bitaye hai, mazak nhi ek aisa time nhi yaad aa rha jab aapke saath naa ho. 1st year me pappu bhai ki wajah se dosti hua apna, aur uske baad to humesha saath hi rhe apan. Apna blackbox wala event abhi tk yaad aa rha hai, hm bol rhe the ki aap galat hai aur aap hmko smjha rhe ki nhi hm gadhe hai wo bhi contest ke beech me. Phir aap frustation me bole ruko hm hi code kr dete hai, hm pure time yahi bolte rhe ki nhi chalega nhi chalega, phir jab saara test case pass hua to kya mazza aaaya tha bhai. Deserving 3rd the us din xD. Puure saal aapko bolte reh gaye chaliye ESC ka labs kr lete hai lakin aap gadhe ke bachhe chale hi nhi.  Arreyy aur MTH me ‚ÄúKarma‚Äù wala B to kaise hi bhul sakte hai. Yaad hai apna election me kaise aap ‚Äúunofficial‚Äù campaigning kar rahe the. Har jagah saath gaye the bhai, ussi ki wajah se darr khatam hua tha apna shi bole to. Abhi bhi yaad hai jeetne ka baat sabse pehle aapko hi bole the. Kitna bakwaas movie sab dikhane le gaye hai yaar hmko aap, jagga jasoos, baadshaho, all the best, bas corona ki wajah se aapke fav sallu bhai ka movies reh gaya. Aur wo wala contest yaad hai, jisme hm apan ke team ka katwa kr aaye the, bhai bahut life lesson diye hai yaar aap hmko. I guess abhi bahut aur bacha hai future me. Aur bhai CSE ke courses me kya hi masti kiye hai. 2nd year me aap bol diye the ek bhi CSE ka course as OE nhi krenge, aur ab thoda apna transcript dekhiye to. Etna emotional blackmail krwa krwa ke aapko saara CSE ka course sab uthwaye hai. Aaj tk kayede se ek coding wala assignment kiye hai aap, wo bhi kyuki ghar pr the, haskell me cipher. Har course me koi na koi mast sa memory hai apna to, OS me wo subah wala quiz jisme mera naam likh diye the, Nitin Saxena ke class me bahar sofa pr baithna, CS201 ka chessmaster wala question, CS220 ka labs, Networks ke endsem me 110% sure wala wrong answer, Compiler ka endsem ( Nahi bhulenge ye to ), Comp Physics ka pehla lab :p ‚Ä¶ Aur wo CSO me to kya pass karwye hai. Chapwa ke top hi kara diye. Aur apna BSBE ke late night ‚Äútours‚Äù aur end me race to kya hi tha. Waise kuch nhi to aapko git use krna to sikha hi diye ye 4 saal me. Arreyy aur haan ‚ÄúSab khana khake daaru peeke chale gaye, sab chale gaye‚Äù >> ‚ÄúSonu‚Äù ü§™. Aapko ek football ka game khelwane ke liye naya chaddi khareed ke laye the hm. Aur apna unexplainable 1k wala base to zindagi bhar rahega xD. ‚ÄúAaj codeforces pr virtual dijiyega kya?‚Äù Although eska answer humesha pata rehta hai hmko, still baar baar puchne ka alag hi mazza hai.

Har chota se chota problem aap tk le gaye hai yaar. Bahut helpful aur rational aadmi hai aap. Ye college ka life to nhi paar ho pata bhai aapke bina. Mera har bina matlab ka zid manne hai yaar aap. Dil se Thanks bhai sab cheez ke liye, koi aur hota to nhi kr pata bhai shi me. Hm bahut jyada lucky hai aap jaisa bhai mila hmko. Ek cheez reh gaya bas apna to, future me apan same hi company me hoonge to shaam ko aapko mera wingman banna hoga.
PS: Aur haan future me jab hm politician banenege to aapko hi right hand banayenge, yaad rakhiyega :p.
PPS: Aur bsdk, gaali sunna tha naa aapko to suniye bc, aap agar apna teen saal baad wala pact bhule naa to gaand me trishul daal denge. Samjhe naa LoduChand.

text:
Aur Monika, aapko to hm IITk aane se pehle se hi jaante the, Puru Sir ki wajah se. Abhi bhi yaha wale center pr aapka naam laga hua hai xD. Hm dono ka bahut treat reh gaya, lakin ab aana to Hyderabad hi hai. Waha pr pura kasar nikal lenge. Bhul mat jayega bas aap :p. Aur etna game khelne hm bhagwaan ko bolte to wo sakshat darshaan deke bol dete, ki aa jao khel lete hai. Ab to khel lijiye, abhi bhi yaad hai etna bolne pr bhi aap bas ek bakwaas sa chess wala game khele hai :p.
Chaliye all the best for future, windows ko sudharte rahiyega, aur hmlog ko kuch to leak kar hi dijiyega har baar.

author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Bhai Dinesh, mast aadmi hai aap. Aaj tk ek aisa aadmi nhi dekhe hai jo aapka le saka hai, although many have tried and failed. Aaj tk mera etna bejjati kiye hai naa aap, aur wo bhi har baar unique tareeke se. Bas es baat pr etna admiration aa jaata hai naa ki mat puchiye. 1st year me utna jyada baat nhi tha apna, but 2nd year se jo bond bana hai naa ab tk wo zindagi bhar ka hai. Bhai aap wo aadmi the jinko agar hm neend se bhi utha dete the football khelne ke liye bolte the, to kabhi nhi gussa krte the aur humesha maan jaate the. Aur uspr bhi etna dedication field pr mat puchiye. Bhai apan to kitni raat bas cards khelne me bita diye hai, aur kabhi to jeetne diya kijiye apne bhai ko. Aur ye last ka jo ek aur aadha mahina tha wo to best tha bhai. Pehle jab aapka ganda wala kaata quarentine extend hoke tb mazza to bahut aaya, lakin phir jab realize hua ki aap mere wing me nhi hoyega to bahut jayda hi bura laga. Aapke saath to bet bhi laga liye the ki aap nhi aayega, but bhai aap kabhi bhi lagane hi nhi diye ki aap dusre wing me hai. Aur wo quarentine ka aakhri raat to aap hi sambhale the hmko. Bahut mazza aaya tha bhai us din bhi, although jyada yaad nhi hai pr us din apan kitne logo ko chat se girne se bacha liye the xD. Aap etni baar hmko ‚Äòdaaru pilade bhai‚Äô bole hai naa ki mat puchiye. Aur apna pact yaad hai naa, aapko star krte hue dekhna chahte hai hm japanese films me. Mera first ganda movie wahi hoga, to jldi japan jaaye aur banake aaye.  Bahut regret hota hai aapke saath trip pr nhi jaa paye, pr apni ek to trip ab banti hi hai. Bhai sach bataye to campus ka one of the most missed part is aapka wo randomly bejjati kr dena. Love you bhai, kabhi nhi bhula payenge aapko. Aur mazak nhi japan jaake bhule naa to zinda nhi chodenge.
PS: Thoda whatsapp pr disturb krna kam kr diye hai aap, jo hmko jyada acha lag nhi rha. Agar frequency jldi hi badha nhi to ghar me ghus ke maarenge.

text: Aur 4-2, kya haal chaal. Jab aap budhe bhi ho jayega aur us samay tk Esha lemma, Esha theorem, Esha postulates, etc.. sab bhi aa jayega tb bhi aise hi bolenge aapko. Sab ko yahi bolna hai ki ye whi esha hai jo mere se baar baar hari hai. Jo 2 hai wo bhi bas ritesh ki wajah se xD. Aur navratan korma ke bare me to kya hi bole :p. Aapke aur gulati sir ke bina to mazak nhi degree nhi milta hmko. All the best for the future, bade researcher ban ke bhul mat jayega.

text: Thanks for helping in placement, bas.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Aur Bhai Pandey, aapke baare me to kya hi kahe, etna dil ke ache aadmi shayaad hi abhi bhi banate hoonge upar wale. Pehle 1-2 saal me to bas aap ko naam se jaante the, phir shashank aur ritesh ki wajah se apan bhi dost ban gaye. And rest is history. üòÜ Bhai lockdown ke baad se to apan almost daily hi video call kr rhe the, aur kya hi bakwaas krte the. Wo race me daudne wala argument, Naam nhi lene wala .... Kya din the yaar wo. Laga hi nahi ki pandemic chal raha tha, literally aag lagi thi basti me aur hm apni masti me wala case hua tha. 4-5 ghanta daily baat krne me guzar jata tha. Abhi bhi bata dete hai aapko, pehle hi team me le lena chahiye tha, ab to ritesh ke hi team me rehenge humesha üòù. Phir yaha campus me wapas aake to kya hi mazze lete the yaar sab ke. Aap to NLP ke assignments me hi pura time bita diye ("Jaake NLP ka assignment kr le"). Khair aapke wajah se at least volleyball to phir se khel liye. Aur apna late night Hall 9 ka chakkar lagane ka to kya hi bole. Pura chaar saal ek hi raat me discuss kr liye the apan log. Kya bitching kiye the us raat üòà. Bahut ‚ÄúGyaan‚Äù diye hai aap hmko zindagi ka. IG abhi bahut baaki bhi hai, so milke batate rahiyega. Gadhe Bokaro me rahte hai, kabhi ghar bhi aa jaya kijiye. Waise chahe aapko kitna bhi bol le company nhi change krwane ke liye, bahut help kiye the yaar mera us waqt. Thanks yaar pandey sab cheez ke liye. <3 

PS: Love You Too Pandey :)
PPS: Always remember 9.16 19:57
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Kussu bhai, mast aadmi hai aap. Aap se etne baar bas ‚Äúangrezi shi‚Äù krwane ke liye call kiye hai naa, mat puchiye. Humesha bina kuch bole maan jaate the aap to, bahut maddad kiye hai bhai. Apna dosti to first year me pappu bhaye ki wajah se hua tha. Us samay to kya hi masti krte the apan. Apna first year wala site Ripe Cucumbers kya shi tha, abhi tk mere github pr hai. Mera one and only ‚Äúfight club‚Äù victory aapke against hi hai, 100% win rate hai apna xD. Aur wo pizza bet kaise bhul sakte hai, 2 large non-veg pizza khilwaye the aap. Apan 4 saal me jitna bet lagye hoonge utna to shayaad hi koi lagaya hoga. Abhi waise ek aur bacha hai, kabhi US me aake uska bhi liya jayega. Mohawk hairstyle is still onnn. Aur campus ka last month to humesha memorable rahega. Wo din abhi bhi yaad hai jis din aapka Stanford me hua tha, andr se aisa khushi ho rha tha ki jaise mera hi ho gya ho. Uske baad aapka pura future me clubs ka planning kiye the hm log xD. College choose krne ke liye bhi kitna lamba discussions kiye the apan. Aur aap wo pehle aadmi the jo mere se ‚Äòlodu‚Äô sune the. This will go to your tombstone. Wo din yaad hai jab hm aapko gila krne ke liye apne hi bed pr paani daal diye the xD. Saath me football khelne me bhi bahut mazza aaya. Aur Fifa me to kya haarte the bhai, bahar jaane se pehle atleast thoda apna Fifa skills badhaye bhai. Waise aapse jyada ache se work life balance manage krne wala koi banda nhi dekhe hai. Aur ekdum practical bande hai aap, this is the best quality jiske liye hm aapke pass aate rhenge for major life decisions. Best of luck aage ke liye, IK ki aap world ke best statistician baniyega ya ek so so professor :p. Bahar jaake bhul mat jayega, I have a feeling ki dono end me ek hi city me kaam krenge ;). Aur Fifa 40 tk bhi hum hi better hoonge :p.

PS: I thought I would write this in English, but phir ‚Äúangrezi shi‚Äù kaun hi krta.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text: Aur chota jindal. Aapke saath to kitna masti kiye hai bhai, college me football se leke pubg tk. Jab bhi football khelne jaate the, aap kya tez daudte the aur phir hm jab goalkeeping me hagg dete tha, edhar tk aake sunate the. Aapko to jitne baar khelne bulate the utne baar aa hi jaate the. Aapko chidhane me bhi kitna mazza aata tha hmko, aap ekdum gussa ho jaate the xD. Pubg me bhi har baar mere se samaan leke hi khelte the aap to :p, mere bina game hi kaha acha hota tha aapka. Aur last ka mahina bhi kya hi mast tha, puure mahine aap to mere hi saath soye. Starting me to pura guard se darte rehte the, end aate aate wo bhi seekh hi gaya lol. Aur bhai aap to shi me humesha mere side rehte the, chahe kuch bhi ho jaye. Ye shashank aur ritesh opposite ho jaye phir bhi. Mazedaar tha wo sab time bhi. Among Us ka wo sab session sab bhi yaad hai, kaise camera me baith ke dekhte rehte the har time. All the best bhai for the future, apan to milte hi rhenge kabhi na kabhi trips pr.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Ram bhai, mast aadmi hai aap to. Acha hai apna dosti ho gya hai pappu bhai ki wajah se ho gya, uske baad to alag mazze kiye hai apan. 1st year me SoC ke time mile the apan, us samy se hi suna rhe hai aap hmko. CSE wale to saare courses apan saath hi kiye hai. Sab me alag level masti tha, mera OS wala jo quiz me naam likh kr aa gaye. Phir apan jo Lab wale course me jo masti kiye the, ek raat pehle aapko almost nachwa hi diye the xD, aur phir agle din sir se kya daant khaye the. Aur wo ML wale raat me to bhai kaise hi bhul sakte hai, bade hooke bhi gaali suniyega jab bhi wo yaad aayega lol. Compiler me to alag level josh me aaye the aap, pura hi likh daale the. Last do sem offline hi tha, lakin apna baat to jaari hi tha puure time. Yaad hai December me kaise aap pura ‚Äúlove guru‚Äù types advice de rhe the. üòÇ yaha se xD tk ka safar saath me chale hai apan lol. Apne messeges me aadha se jyada yahi ss forward hota tha. Aur bhai aapke gaaliyon me kya consistency rehta hai, aaj bhi jab gadhe ke bachhe bolte to background me aapka ‚ÄòB**k‚Äô sunayi deta hai. Aapko bhai kitna bhi sunate hai aap kabhi bhi gussa nhi krte the, ulta wapas gaali dete the. Ye baat to sabse acha lagta hai aapka to. Pure covid ke dauran, aap aur abhishek ka grp me baap bete ka ladai was the most interesting part of those days. Har baar jab bhi grp kholte ek smile ke saath grp band krte the.Thanks bhai sab cheez ke liye, aise hi message krte rahiyega. Aur haan kabhi Samsung Korea jaane ka mauka mila, aur aap waha somehow chaap diye, to daily video call kijyega :p.

text:
Liti mere bhai, mazze hi aa gaye aapke saath to. Time kaise nikla en chaar saalo me, samjh hi nhi aaya. Aap literally jhele hai humko. Kabhi kisi cheez ke liye mana nhi kiye bhai, kaise kr lete hai yaar ye?üòá Hmko first year se life lesson de rhe hai aap. Kitni saari yaadein judi hai aapke saath. First year me wo bio ke pehle wala raat kya dara diye the. Summer of code me bhi kya masti krte the yaar hum log. Site ko bas sundar bana rhe the xD. 2 mahina pura guzar gaya git aur javascript CSS ke alawa kuch nhi seekhe the. Electronics wala course sirf aapki wajah se nikal gaya hai bhai, apna neend kharaab krke hmko padhaye the aap, wo bhi exam ke just pehle. Us din se hi alag respect aa gaya bhai. Daily subah uthate the hmko, class le jaane ke liye. Thermo wala quiz yaad hai, bina bole aap mera quiz likh kr aa gaye. Apan CS202 me kya chaape the apne assignments, 1st the, aur ‚Äúkoi‚Äù bahut jal bhi gaya tha es baat se üòù. CSE wale courses me to bahut memory hai apni Wo DS Algo me debug krna, TOC ka assignments in the Library, Algo 2 me class ke bahar baithna, CS201 ka wo chessmaster wala sawal‚Ä¶ Aapki wajah se at least mera assignments to time pr submit ho hi jaata tha. Aapko aur Anany ko kitna emotional blackmail krna padta tha koi CSE ka course OE me lene ke liye, sab acha hua tha waise üòí.  Arreyy aur apan jab football khelne ke liye ek dusre ko leke jaate the bhai, epic tha. Humesha plan apne hi room se shuru hota tha, kabhi aapko mann krta tha kabhi hmko xD. Arrey aur wo TT me jo Esha ko serve krna sikha diye the naa ussi ki wajah se apna bada nuksaan ho gya tha. Aur jo hmlog daily canteen jaate the bhai, aap to ek do cheez kha ke aa jate the, hm josh josh me pura menu hi order kr dete the. Bas aapki wajah se mote hue hai hm üòà . Wo TOC ke exam ke pehle jo raat bhar TV series sab dekhe the, aur agle subah seating arrangement ka shock to zindagi bhar yaad rahega. Waise dekha jaaye to mera rom com dekhne ka aadat aa hi lagwaye hai. Etna jyada hindi TV series dekhe hai naaa apan saath me, aur aap gadhe abhi tk HIMYM khatam nhi kiye üòè. Aur bhai apna late night walks sab to epic hi tha. Kya mast discussion chalta tha, aur kabhi kabhi to raat bhar apan log baat hi krte reh jaate the. Mera bahut secrets pata hai aapko, bata mat dijiyega kabhi bhi kisi ko üôè.  Ye corona wala lockdown se abhi tk, yaad nhi hai hmko ek bhi din jis din apan, pandey aur aapka video call naa hua ho. Kya bakwaas cheez pr ladte rehte the yaar hmlog. Aur haan aapka youtube ke recommendations ke to kya hi kehne hai, 2 saal bas aapka gaana sunte sunte guzar gaya, bahut miss krte hai yaar wo abhi bhi.

Sab cheez me kuch positive dekhna sikhaye hai yaar aap zindagi me. Aapki dosti ekdum invaluable hai, college ke sabse ache moments aap aur anany ke saath bitaye hai. Aur yaar chahe log jo bole, aapka kisi ko bhi nhi mana kr paana aapka sabse bada strength hai bhai. Kisi bhi time pr bhale hi hm aapko kitna bhi pareshaan kiye ho ya aap kitna bhi frustated ho, I can always look up to you aur aap turant mera madad krne aa jate hai bina apna kuch soche. Idk hm kya punya kiye ho pichle janam, but ussi ka nateeja hai aap jaisa dost. Aapke jaisa dost once in a lifetime milta hai, so aapko chodd dene ka to point hi nhi banta. Dekhiye ab google ka location final to hai hi but still, pata nhi kyu hmko to dil se lagta hai ki apan abhi nhi to future me saath me hi hoonge koi company me. Aur kaynat to acha hi kaam krta hai apne case me to dekh lijiye. üòÇ Best of luck bhai future ke liye, bikul change mat hoyega.

PS: Finally mera acha ho jayega stopstalk pr rating dekh lijiyega :p.
PPS: Apna team to confirm hi rahega hamesha ke liye, chahe aur koi lily hi kyu naa aa jaye.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text: Shashank bhai, aapke baare me to kya hi likhe. 1st year ka summers was the best. Bhai kitna masti kiye hai apan log, hm hi jante hai. Etna saara movies, aur match sab saath dekhe hai ki mat puchiye. Har barca ka bada victory pr sabse pehle aapko hi call kiye hai aaj tk aur future me bhi krenge. Bahut mazak udaye hai aap mera, but still jab bhi zindagi me koi bhi problem hota hai, sirf aapke pass jaate hai. IDK par hamesha aisa feeling aata hai ki aapse related ho ya na ho aap kuch na kuch kr hi dijiyega. Future me bhi hamesha aapke pass aate rhenge. Aapke saath alag level ka connect banta hai. Mere GPL me sabse jyada excited aap hi rehte the, ye pyaar nhi to kya hai :p. Aur bhai apna BBQ wala breaks to world famous hai, agla bbq party me bhi chalte hai. Sports me to apna pasand same hi hai har jagah. Chahe wo RCB ho ya Barca. Mera aadha se jyada naya kapda aap hi pehle try kiye hai :p. Waise upar se aap jitna bhi bol le, aap humesha ye cheez ka dhyaan rakhte the ki kahi hmko kuch problem to naa ho rha hai. IITk me you were the big brother I never had before, but I needed. Apna Qatar ka Fifa World Cup aur Phir Barca ka trip is Onn.  Best of Luck bhai future ke liye, mast baniyega aap I know it.

text:
Bhole Baba ki Jai!
Kothari Sir, aapke baare me to kya hi bole. IITk aane ke pehle hi aapke bahut charche sun rakhe the, Jamshedpur me ek chaapu banda hai jo aa rha hai hmare saath hi padhne. Milwaye to hmko pandey ji hi the, lakin phir aage to aapse baat krne me mazza hi aa gaya. Jab bhi hall 5 aate the to aapse jrur milke jaate the agar aap hote the room pr to. Aur wo shiv ji ki bhakti wali raat kaise bhul sakte hai, apan to US/Europe me bhi saath me bhakti krenge. Alag level feel aaya tha us din, aur aap pura pros and cons samjha rhe the hmko xD. Bas aapki wajah se hi hmko 2nd year me London ghumne ka mauka mila, aap hi pura motivate kiye the cold mailing krne ke liye. Aur apan ka to kya discussions chalta tha over lunch, wo veg vs non veg wala yaad hai. Aap almost mana hi diye the veg banne ke liye, phir ek fried chicken pura argument hi jeet gaya :p. Aur mere dabbe pr arch bhi bas aapke baar baar fayeda batane ki wajah se install kiye hai. Aap bahut chaapu aadmi hai, best of luck for the future, bhul mat jaayega bade aadmi banke.
